6af:SEED/reSpec.md:172:  - **Living sections**: `## OVERVIEW`, `## STAGES`, `## TASKS` (overwritable)\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/reSpec.md:175:- `C_Distribute.md` — **Living**: Distribution and release strategy. Contains `C1/C2/C3` as sections:\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/reSpec.md:229:- **Required action:** Review the seed identity file (`SEED/<seed>.md`) for completeness and consistency with A/B sections.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/reSpec.md:375:`B_Develop.md` is the single governed execution hub. It contains overwritable planning sections and an append-only canonical log.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/reSpec.md:548:- **Required fields:** Each DUP entry must specify the exact target (file + section + sentence/line anchor) and the change intent.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/reSpec.md:549:- **Suggested wording (recommended):** To make approval actionable, the LLM SHOULD include the exact suggested wording (as short bullets) inside `change_intent` or immediately below it in the same DUP entry.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/snapshot.md:7:status_1p: Design scope aligned to latest API: endpoints /v1/health, /v1/config, /v1/chart, /v1/transit, /v1/timeline; chart types include natal/moment/solar_arc/secondary_progression; timelines unified for transit/secondary_progression/solar_arc with lunations/eclipses tokens.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SEED/snapshot.md:12:- Remove legacy fields (metadata.name, subject, settings.points.lilith, metadata.output/level/body/step_years).\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SPEC/A_Design.md:6:- constraints: Python 3.12 target; FastAPI/Uvicorn; Swiss Ephemeris as source of truth; UTC timestamps; location object required; deterministic rounding to 2 decimals for chart/transit outputs; lunations/eclipses sourced from CSV; adaptive timeline scan; legacy fields removed.\n0996e30f2b94a17f9d3fb02569e171403e7b46af:SPE