bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:156:  - **SEED respec point**: includes `SEED/`\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:157:  - **SPEC respec point**: includes `SEED/ + SPEC/`\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:158:  - **SPIN respec point**: includes `SEED/ + SPEC/ + SPIN/`\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:166:- `A_Design.md` — **Living**: Design-layer operating brief and decomposition. Contains `A1/A2/A3` as sections:\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:171:- `B_Develop.md` — **Hybrid (Living + Log sections)**: Implementation strategy + execution hub. Contains:\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:172:  - **Living sections**: `## OVERVIEW`, `## STAGES`, `## TASKS` (overwritable)\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:175:- `C_Distribute.md` — **Living**: Distribution and release strategy. Contains `C1/C2/C3` as sections:\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:229:- **Required action:** Review the seed identity file (`SEED/<seed>.md`) for completeness and consistency with A/B sections.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:375:`B_Develop.md` is the single governed execution hub. It contains overwritable planning sections and an append-only canonical log.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:548:- **Required fields:** Each DUP entry must specify the exact target (file + section + sentence/line anchor) and the change intent.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/reSpec.md:549:- **Suggested wording (recommended):** To make approval actionable, the LLM SHOULD include the exact suggested wording (as short bullets) inside `change_intent` or immediately below it in the same DUP entry.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/snapshot.md:7:status_1p: Design scope aligned to latest API: endpoints /v1/health, /v1/config, /v1/chart, /v1/transit, /v1/timeline; chart types include natal/moment/solar_arc/secondary_progression; timelines unified for transit/secondary_progression/solar_arc with lunations/eclipses tokens.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SEED/snapshot.md:12:- Remove legacy fields (metadata.name, subject, settings.points.lilith, metadata.output/level/body/step_years).\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/A_Design.md:6:- constraints: Python 3.12 target; FastAPI/Uvicorn; Swiss Ephemeris as source of truth; UTC timestamps; location object required; deterministic rounding to 2 decimals for chart/transit outputs; lunations/eclipses sourced from CSV; adaptive timeline scan; legacy fields removed.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/A_Design.md:8:- key_decisions: Unify timelines under /v1/timeline; restrict /v1/transit to transit only; remove astrocartography/synastry/on_natal/progression_timeline; remove subject/metadata.name/settings.points.lilith and other legacy fields.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/A_Design.md:24:- removed_fields: metadata.name, subject, settings.points.lilith, metadata.output, metadata.level/body/step_years, transit_type on_natal/synastry/astrocartography/solar_arc/secondary_progression.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/B_Develop.md:23:- goal: Implement /v1/chart (natal/moment) and /v1/config with deterministic outputs; include aspects.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/B_Develop.md:26:  - /v1/config catalogs include defaults\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/B_Develop.md:469:  - Outer planets excluded from progression timeline.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/B_Develop.md:548:  - Align design/seed scope to latest API: /v1/health, /v1/config, /v1/chart, /v1/transit, /v1/timeline; chart types include natal/moment/solar_arc/secondary_progression; unify timelines and remove deprecated modes/endpoints.\ndb36e632d7149013ea5598bb48dff8b71d074a08:SPEC/B_Develop.md:549:  - Remove legacy fields and tighten request/response descr