md:175:- `C_Distribute.md` — **Living**: Distribution and release strategy. Contains `C1/C2/C3` as sections:\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/reSpec.md:229:- **Required action:** Review the seed identity file (`SEED/<seed>.md`) for completeness and consistency with A/B sections.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/reSpec.md:375:`B_Develop.md` is the single governed execution hub. It contains overwritable planning sections and an append-only canonical log.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/reSpec.md:548:- **Required fields:** Each DUP entry must specify the exact target (file + section + sentence/line anchor) and the change intent.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/reSpec.md:549:- **Suggested wording (recommended):** To make approval actionable, the LLM SHOULD include the exact suggested wording (as short bullets) inside `change_intent` or immediately below it in the same DUP entry.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/snapshot.md:7:status_1p: Design scope aligned to latest API: endpoints /v1/health, /v1/config, /v1/chart, /v1/transit, /v1/timeline; chart types include natal/moment/solar_arc/secondary_progression; timelines unified for transit/secondary_progression/solar_arc with lunations/eclipses tokens.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SEED/snapshot.md:12:- Remove legacy fields (metadata.name, subject, settings.points.lilith, metadata.output/level/body/step_years).\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/A_Design.md:6:- constraints: Python 3.12 target; FastAPI/Uvicorn; Swiss Ephemeris as source of truth; UTC timestamps; location object required; deterministic rounding to 2 decimals for chart/transit outputs; lunations/eclipses sourced from CSV; adaptive timeline scan; legacy fields removed.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/A_Design.md:8:- key_decisions: Unify timelines under /v1/timeline; restrict /v1/transit to transit only; remove astrocartography/synastry/on_natal/progression_timeline; remove subject/metadata.name/settings.points.lilith and other legacy fields.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/A_Design.md:24:- removed_fields: metadata.name, subject, settings.points.lilith, metadata.output, metadata.level/body/step_years, transit_type on_natal/synastry/astrocartography/solar_arc/secondary_progression.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:23:- goal: Implement /v1/chart (natal/moment) and /v1/config with deterministic outputs; include aspects.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:26:  - /v1/config catalogs include defaults\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:469:  - Outer planets excluded from progression timeline.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:548:  - Align design/seed scope to latest API: /v1/health, /v1/config, /v1/chart, /v1/transit, /v1/timeline; chart types include natal/moment/solar_arc/secondary_progression; unify timelines and remove deprecated modes/endpoints.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:549:  - Remove legacy fields and tighten request/response descriptions to current shapes (transit only, timeline bodies, lunations/eclipses tokens).\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPEC/B_Develop.md:552:  - Updated SPEC/A_Design.md and SPEC/B_Develop.md to reflect unified timelines, transit-only, and removed legacy fields.\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPIN/docs/contract-first-rebuild-report.md:17:- `SPIN/styx-api/app/main.py` (router include only)\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPIN/docs/contract-first-rebuild-report.md:62:      \"output\": { \"verbosity\": \"normal\", \"astrological_objects\": [\"natal\"] }\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPIN/docs/contract.json:19:      \"astrological_objects\": \"Optional allowlist of named output blocks to include in responses.\",\n8e2fb4cd4f9fe939a071e02cdf31cafc22a0672b:SPIN/docs/contract.json:45:      \"output\": { 